c: 3
v: 199
t: "Mu by’ukuri mu bahawe ibitabo harimo abemera Allah n’ibyo mwahishuriwe (Qur’an) ndetse n’ibyo bahishuriwe (Tawurati n’Ivanjili); bibombarika imbere ya Allah. Ntibagurana amagambo ya Allah indonke (n’ubwo zaba) nke; abo bazahabwa ingororano zabo kwa Nyagasani wabo. Kandi mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubanguka mu ibarura"